description.en: Select your investor type. Be sure to select the correct type, as you cannot change your selection once you start filling out your information in the next steps of the onboarding process.

description.en: To complete your digital onboarding, we are obliged by law to process a symbolic payment to our custodian bank, transferred from an account under your name. A minimum amount of one Euro or USD is sufficient for this. Please note that the amount will be credited to your customer account.
